---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <main class="container" style="padding: 3rem 0;">
    <section class="card glow" style="padding: 2rem;">
      <h1 style="margin:0;">About</h1>
      <p class="muted" style="margin-top: .75rem;">
        Hi! I’m Pranjal Namdeo — transitioning into AI/ML engineering. Previously at Goldman Sachs, I built Python automation and document-processing pipelines that saved significant manual effort.
      </p>

      <div style="display:flex; gap:.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-top: 1rem;">
        <span class="tag">Python</span>
        <span class="tag">SQL</span>
        <span class="tag">Git</span>
        <span class="tag">Data Pipelines</span>
        <span class="tag">Doc Processing</span>
        <span class="tag">OpenCV (Fundamentals and Image Processing in Python)</span>
        <span class="tag">OpenCV (Advanced)</span>
        <span class="tag">PyTorch/TensorFlow</span>
        <span class="tag">Deep Learning with TensorFlow and keras</span>
        <span class="tag">Deep Learning with PyTorch2.x</span>
        <span class="tag">Advanced Image Processing with Deep Learning & Transformers</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
      <h2>Selected Work</h2>

      <!-- Project Card Template -->
      <div class="card" style="padding: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
        <h3 style="margin:0;"><b>Document Information Extraction Pipeline (OCR + Parsing)</h3></b>
        <p class="muted" style="margin:.5rem 0 0;">Proto-NLP style extraction system for key attributes from unstructured documents.</p>

        <ul class="markdown" style="margin-top: .75rem;">
          <li><b>Problem:</b> Manual extraction was slow and error-prone.</li>
          <li><b>Approach:</b> OCR + rule-based parsing + validation checks for edge cases.</li>
          <li><b>Tools:</b> Python, regex, PDF/OCR tooling, pandas.</li>
          <li><b>Outcome:</b> Faster turnaround and consistent extraction.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
      <h2>Skills</h2>
      <div class="card" style="padding: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
        <p style="margin:0;"><b>Core:</b> Python, pandas/NumPy, matplotlib, seaborn, APIs, Git</p>
        <p style="margin:.5rem 0 0;"><b>ML:</b> scikit-learn, PyTorch, TensorFlow (actively building)</p>
        <p style="margin:.5rem 0 0;"><b>AI:</b> Neural Networks,Deep Learning, Transformers, LLMs (actively building), Agentic AI with CrewAi & Langchain</p>
        <p style="margin:.5rem 0 0;"><b>CV:</b> OpenCV (CVIP), image processing fundamentals, Advanced image processing</p>
        <p style="margin:.5rem 0 0;"><b>Docs/NLP-adjacent:</b> OCR, regex extraction, XML parsing</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>